## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f37c6-103">應用程式設定屬性具有在應用程式或使用者層級為基礎的範圍。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f37c6-103">Application settings properties have a scope that is based either at the application or the user level.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f37c6-104">依照提示類別，應用程式範圍的設定屬性則會顯示統一的值給所有使用者的應用程式，而使用者範圍的屬性具有專用應用程式的每個使用者的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f37c6-104">As the categories imply, application-scoped settings properties present uniform values to all users of the application, whereas user-scoped properties have dedicated values for each user of the application.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f37c6-105"><xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationScopedSettingAttribute>表示屬性，應視為應用程式層級設定，而且適當的儲存體的決策都應該據此進行設定提供者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f37c6-105">The <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationScopedSettingAttribute> indicates that a property should be considered an application-level setting, and that appropriate storage decisions should be made accordingly by the settings provider.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f37c6-106">需要為每個設定屬性的領域屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f37c6-106">A scope attribute is required for each settings property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f37c6-107">如果屬性不會套用與<xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationScopedSettingAttribute>或<xref:System.Configuration.UserScopedSettingAttribute>，設定提供者無法辨識的屬性，它便不會序列化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f37c6-107">If a property is not applied with either a <xref:System.Configuration.ApplicationScopedSettingAttribute> or <xref:System.Configuration.UserScopedSettingAttribute>, the property is not recognized by the settings provider—it is not serialized.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f37c6-108">是無效的不過，若要將這兩個屬性套用至相同的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f37c6-108">It is invalid, however, to apply both attributes to the same property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f37c6-109">這類的嘗試會導致<xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationErrorsException>擲回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f37c6-109">Such an attempt will cause a <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationErrorsException> to be thrown.</span></span>  
  
